 <text id="F3024T">
  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>Demus talks about the difficulties of sending mail home.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    <head>
     <name type="recipient">Mary Jane Demus</name>
    </head>

    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1865-02-01"><orig reg="February">Febury</orig> the 1st 65</date>
      <name type="place">Morris <orig reg="island">iland</orig> south <orig reg="Carolina"
       >Carlina</orig></name>
     </dateline>
     <salute><orig reg="My">Mi</orig> Dear</salute>
    </opener>

    <p>this <orig reg="evening">eaving</orig> i set <orig reg="myself">Mi Celf</orig> Down to inform
     you that i am Well at present and hope When <orig reg="these">thes</orig>
     <orig reg="few">feu</orig> lines Reach you <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="May">Ma</orig> find you in the <orig reg="same">sam</orig> state of health a <orig
      reg="My">Mi</orig> Dear how happy i felt <orig reg="When">Whean</orig> i <orig reg="Receive"
      >Receave</orig>
     <orig reg="your">yor</orig> kind letter this Day and <orig reg="found">fond</orig> out that you
     Was Well and all the <orig reg="friends">frends</orig></p>

    <p>But i am <orig reg="very">verry</orig>
     <orig reg="sorry">sory</orig> to say that i <orig reg="have">heave</orig> not <orig reg="heard"
      >hird</orig>
     <orig reg="from">frum</orig> the <orig reg="Boys">Bose</orig> yet but i think that <orig
      reg="they">tha</orig> Will all Be Back <orig reg="soon">son</orig> but i <orig reg="Can't"
      >Cant</orig> tell how <orig reg="soon">son</orig>
     <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="Will">Well</orig>
     <orig reg="Come">Cum</orig> back</p>

    <p>But as <orig reg="soon">son</orig> as <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="Come">Cum</orig> back <orig reg="Why">Wiy</orig> i Will <orig reg="Write"
     >Rite</orig> and let you <orig reg="Know">Now</orig> how you <orig reg="are">ar</orig>
     <orig reg="getting">geting</orig> but i <orig reg="hope">hoppe</orig> and trust that you <orig
      reg="Can't">Cant</orig> get <orig reg="along">a long</orig> till i get <orig reg="home">hom</orig>
     <orig reg="for">fer</orig>
     <orig reg="my">mi</orig> Dear you Must Not think that i think hard of it <orig reg="Because"
      >Becos</orig> i <orig reg="Write">Rite</orig> to you that i <orig reg="Can't">Cant</orig> get
      <orig reg="any">eny</orig> letter <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i Will <orig reg="excuse"
     >excus</orig> you <orig reg="for">fer</orig> it</p>

    <p>For the <orig reg="Mail">Mall</orig> has Not <orig reg="been">bean</orig> Coming <orig
      reg="Regularly">Regely</orig> but think god <orig reg="for">fer</orig> What i get <orig
      reg="from">frum</orig> you But i am happy to say that i <orig reg="Receive">Receave</orig>
     <orig reg="your">yor</orig> letters that had the <orig reg="postage stamps">poaststamps</orig>
     in and i <orig reg="Was">Wos</orig> very Much <orig reg="obliged">a blige</orig> to you for
     sending them.</p>

    <p>But you <orig reg="Wanted">Wontede</orig> Me to send you a New <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
     <unclear>giph</unclear> But <orig reg="My">Mi</orig> Dear i am sorry to say that i <orig
      reg="have">heave</orig> Nothing to send to you this <orig reg="time">tim</orig>
     <orig reg="for">fer</orig> a present But <orig reg="again">a gane</orig> i <orig reg="Write"
      >Rite</orig>
     <orig reg="again">a gane</orig>
     <orig reg="Why">Wiy</orig> i Will try and have <orig reg="something">soming</orig>
     <orig reg="for">fer</orig> you</p>

    <p><orig reg="For">Fer</orig> every thing is so <unclear>Cars</unclear> that i <orig reg="Can't"
      >Cant</orig>
     <unclear>geting</unclear>
     <orig reg="at all">a tall</orig> to send to you But i think i Will try and send you a Box of
      <unclear>Cheal</unclear> as <orig reg="soon">son</orig> as i Can <orig reg="My">Mi</orig> Dear
     a how <orig reg="often">ofton</orig> i set in <orig reg="My">Mi</orig> tent at Night and study
      <orig reg="about">a Boute</orig> you and then think of the long <orig reg="time">tim</orig>
     that I <orig reg="have">heaft</orig> to stay <orig reg="away">a Way</orig>
     <orig reg="from">frum</orig> you</p>

    <p>a <orig reg="sometime">som tim</orig> you <orig reg="Don't">Dont</orig>
     <orig reg="Know">Now</orig> how Bad i <orig reg="feel">fealle</orig></p>

    <p>But you Must <orig reg="excuse">excus</orig> this Bad <orig reg="Writing">Riten</orig>
     <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i am in a <orig reg="hurry">hiry</orig> to get it <orig reg="Wrote"
      >Route</orig> to you in this <orig reg="Mail">Male</orig> give <orig reg="My">Mi</orig> love
     to all the <orig reg="friends">frends</orig> and <orig reg="My">Mi</orig> Best love to <orig
      reg="yourself">yor Celf</orig></p>

    <closer>
     <salute/>
     <signed>Mr. D. A. Demus to Mrs. D. A. Demus</signed>
     <seg type="postscript">
      <orig reg="My">Mi</orig> Dear and <orig reg="true">tru</orig> Wife <orig reg="No">Now</orig>
      <orig reg="More">Mor</orig><lb/>
      <orig reg="Write">Rite</orig>
      <orig reg="Soon">Son</orig> to Morris <orig reg="island">iland</orig> South <orig
       reg="Carolina">Carlina</orig><lb/><lb/> all the <orig reg="postage stamps">poaststamps</orig>
      that you sent to Me <orig reg="Why">Wiy</orig> somebody stole <orig reg="from">frum</orig> Me
     </seg>
    </closer>
   </div1>
  </body>
